        <h2 property="dc:title">
    Anatomy of Ferguson’s Police Riot    </h2>
        <div class="article-teaser"><p>The official response to Michael Brown&rsquo;s murder has laid bare the cheapness of black life.</p>
</div>
    
  <div class="views-field-value byline">
    <a href="/authors/purvi-shah"><span property="dc:creator">Purvi Shah</span></a>  </div><!--/views-field-value-->
  <div class="article-info-string">
    <span class="article-date">August 21, 2014</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;
      </div><!--/article info string-->
  <div class="item-list"><ul class="tweet-string clear clearfix"><li class="first"><a 
  style="background: #eceef5;
-webkit-border-radius: 3px;
border: 1px solid #cad4e7;
cursor: pointer;
padding: 2px 2px 2px;
white-space: nowrap;
color: #3b5998;
float:right;"
  href="#" 
  onclick="
    window.open(
      'https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u='+encodeURIComponent(location.href), 
      'facebook-share-dialog', 
      'width=626,height=436'); 
    return false;"><i 
    style="background-image: url(/sites/default/modules/custom/nation_theme/facebook_icon.png);
background-size: auto;
