<div class="entry blurb">
  <a href="/video/181527/are-americas-police-departments-waging-war-black-bodies" class="imagecache imagecache-tiny_thumbnail_33x22 imagecache-linked imagecache-tiny_thumbnail_33x22_linked"><img src="http://www.thenation.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/tiny_thumbnail_33x22/ferguson_protest_police_tape_ap_mthumb.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-tiny_thumbnail_33x22" width="33" height="22" /></a>  <a href="/video/181527/are-americas-police-departments-waging-war-black-bodies">WATCH: Are America’s Police Departments Waging a War on Black Bodies?</a></div><!--/entry-->
  
      

  </div>
